{"tid":2048144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北京中醫法，要向藍絲文宣","createTime":"2020-06-02T14:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T14:58:48.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6f6f8b123d2c978ff907125fa0ec73c964d7a6","tid":2048144,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"要佢地明白自己撐緊咩<br />\n<br />\n《北京市中醫藥條例（草案）》：<br />\n36）不得以任何方式或者行為詆毀、污衊中醫藥<br />\n54）詆毀、污衊中醫藥......由公安機關依法給予治安管理處罰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtCYJ12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtCYJ12.jpg&h=27e0cce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://wjw.beijing.gov.cn/hdjl_20203/myzj/202005/t20200530_1911882.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwjw.beijing.gov.cn%2Fhdjl_20203%2Fmyzj%2F202005%2Ft20200530_1911882.html&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=722be9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wjw.beijing.gov.cn/hdjl_20203/myzj/202005/t20200530_1911882.html</a>"}]}